OL,3,CLarge fire at a former convent in
OL,4,CDownpatrick started 'deliberately'
OL,6,FFirefighters have put out a blaze at a
OL,7,Fformer convent in Downpatrick after a
OL,8,F15-hour operation involving around 70
OL,9,Fofficers.
OL,11,FThe NIFRS were called to the property
OL,12,Fjust after 7pm on Sunday where a
OL,13,Fspokesperson said they were met with
OL,14,F"a well-developed fire" and that "the
OL,15,Fcause is believed to be deliberate".
OL,17,FThe spokesperson added: "A large
OL,18,Fbuilding fire on Irish Street,
OL,19,FDownpatrick, has now been dealt with.
OL,20,FThe initial call was received at
OL,21,F7.01pm on Sunday.
OL,26,@yD@YOU
