OL,3,CLarge fire at a former convent in
OL,4,CDownpatrick started 'deliberately'
OL,6,F"Our Firefighters worked tirelessly
OL,7,Fthroughout the duration of the
OL,8,Fincident to ensure that the fire was
OL,9,Fbrought under control and extinguished.
OL,11,F"We would like to thank the public for
OL,12,Ftheir patience while we dealt with the
OL,13,Fincident. The cause of the fire is
OL,14,Fbelieved to have been deliberate
OL,15,Fignition and the incident was dealt
OL,16,Fwith by 10.03am."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
