OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782751678
OL,3,CLarge fire at a former convent in
OL,4,CDownpatrick started 'deliberately'
OL,6,FSome 70 firefighters were involved,
OL,7,Fusing breathing apparatus,
OL,8,Ffirefighting jets and two aerial
OL,9,Fladder jets, supported by 10
OL,10,Fappliances from towns as far afield as
OL,11,FNewtownards, a Command Support Unit
OL,12,Ffrom Lisburn and a water tanker from
OL,13,FWarrenpoint.
OL,15,FSouth Down SDLP MLA Colin McGrath
OL,16,Fexpressed sadness at the incident at a
OL,17,Fformer convent building.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
