OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782751678
OL,3,CLarge fire at a former convent in
OL,4,CDownpatrick started 'deliberately'
OL,6,FIn a post on social media Mr McGrath
OL,7,Fsaid while the building has "stood
OL,8,Fderelict for some time", it "remains a
OL,9,Fbeautiful and iconic part of our
OL,10,Ftown's skyline", adding: "It is
OL,11,Fheartbreaking to see it like this."
OL,13,FHe also paid tribute to the
OL,14,Ffirefighters who battled to contain
OL,15,Fthe blaze.
OL,17,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Police
OL,18,Fwould ask members of the public to
OL,19,Fkeep away from this area to ensure
OL,20,Feveryone's safety."
